{"word":"G2369 - θυμιαστήριον - thymiastḗrion - thoo-mee-as-tay'-ree-on - Censer","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">θυμιαστήριον</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">thymiastḗrion</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">thoo-mee-as-tay'-ree-on</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Censer</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Noun Neuter / பெயர்ச்சொல் (அஃறிணை)</span>"},{"paragraph":"தூபம்கலசம் - பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"1. a censer"},{"paragraph":"2. the altar of incense"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a derivative of <a href=\"#/G2370 - θυμιάω - thymiáō - thoo-mee-ah'-o/2370\">G2370</a>; a <i>place of fumigation</i>, that is, the <i>altar of incense</i> (in the Temple): - censer.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}